article_id:592,category_name:News,title_name:A Gift of Consecrated Water to Celebrate the Facility Event!,image_path:,message:<div>To celebrate the ongoing facility event, we have sent everyone a gift of 100 consecrated water!</div><div>We hope you use it to upgrade the new wyrmprints and put them to good use during the Flames of Reflection event!</div><div><br></div><div>This gift will be sent to all players who started the game by <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1563429600"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Players can claim it from their goodie boxes for up to seven days after reception. If the gift isn&rsquo;t retrieved within seven days, it will be lost.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost!</div>,start_time:1563429600,update_time1569487261